OL,3,CPartner of businesswoman killed in
OL,4,Croad collision pays tribute to her
OL,6,FThe partner of a woman who died in a
OL,7,Froad traffic collision near Royal
OL,8,FWootton Bassett has paid tribute to
OL,9,Fher.
OL,11,FPet shop owner Barbara Mullaney was
OL,12,Fkilled in the crash on the B4696 at
OL,13,Fjust after 6pm on June 30.
OL,15,FHer partner of more than 46 years,
OL,16,FPatrick Maher, described Barbara as
OL,17,Fthe sort of person "who enjoyed
OL,18,Fhelping people".
OL,20,F"I didn't realise until she died just
OL,21,Fhow much she affected people.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
