OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783698493
OL,3,CPartner of businesswoman killed in
OL,4,Croad collision pays tribute to her
OL,6,F"We had probably two or three rows in
OL,7,F46 years of being together."
OL,9,FMr Maher says Barbara's popularity in
OL,10,Fthe local community of Cricklade where
OL,11,Fher shop, Animal Fayre, is based is
OL,12,Fshown through the amount of flowers
OL,13,Fleft outside the store.
OL,15,F"There are flowers all over the front
OL,16,Fof the shop - they sold out of flowers.
OL,18,F"The fact she was as she was is why
OL,19,Fpeople loved her".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
