OL,3,CPartner of businesswoman killed in
OL,4,Croad collision pays tribute to her
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Ffollowing a road collision near Royal
OL,8,FWootton Bassett that resulted in the
OL,9,Fdeath of a woman in her 70s.
OL,11,FAnthony Howells, 43, of Reids Piece,
OL,12,FPurton, has been charged with murder,
OL,13,Fdangerous driving, driving with no
OL,14,Finsurance, failing to stop at a road
OL,15,Ftraffic collision and failing to
OL,16,Fprovide a sample.
OL,18,FHe was remanded in custody and
OL,19,Fappeared at Swindon Magistrates Court
OL,20,Fyesterday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
