CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783698493
OL,3,CPartner of businesswoman killed in
OL,4,Croad collision pays tribute to her
OL,6,FNo plea was entered in court and he
OL,7,Fwas remanded in custody once again
OL,8,Funtil his next appearance on Wednesday
OL,9,F(8 July) at Bristol Crown Court.
OL,11,FWiltshire Police said the collision
OL,12,Finvolved an orange Peugeot 107
OL,13,Ftravelling southbound and a black
OL,14,FVauxhall Astra travelling northbound.
OL,16,FThe driver of the Peugeot, a woman in
OL,17,Fher 70s, was declared dead at the
OL,18,Fscene.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
