OL,3,CPartner of businesswoman killed in
OL,4,Croad collision pays tribute to her
OL,6,FA passenger in the Vauxhall, a teenage
OL,7,Fgirl, suffered serious injuries in the
OL,8,Fcollision and was taken to hospital
OL,9,Fbefore being discharged.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
